dc_title_s: Soil and Water Districts: Hennepin County, Minnesota
dc_description_s: This dataset contains the Soil and Water District Boundaries in Hennepin County for local elections. Current boundaries are as of the 2002 redistricting for Soil and Water election districts.The field NAME_TXT contains the district identifier for each Soil and Water District. Link to Attribute Table Information: http://gis.hennepin.us/OpenData/Metadata/Soil%20Water%20Districts.pdf Data updated: monthlyUse Limitations: This data (i) is furnished AS IS with no representation as to completeness or accuracy; (ii) is furnished with no warranty of any kind; and (iii) is not suitable for legal, engineering or surveying purposes.
